\itemize{
\item Isotropic diffusion: one mode with weight \eqn{(1)}.
\item Axially symmetric diffusion: three grouped weights
\eqn{(1/5, 2/5, 2/5)}.
\item Fully anisotropic diffusion: five equal weights
